query:
SELECT 
  pwi.id,
  pwi.productName,
  pwi.locationId,
  i.id as inventory_id,
  pr.id as reservation_id,
  pr.pickingOrderId,
  po.customerOrderNumber
FROM pickingWaveItems pwi
LEFT JOIN inventory i ON pwi.locationId = i.locationId
LEFT JOIN pickingReservations pr ON i.id = pr.inventoryId
LEFT JOIN pickingOrders po ON pr.pickingOrderId = po.id
WHERE pwi.waveId = (SELECT id FROM pickingWaves ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 1)
LIMIT 10;
